<p style="text-align: justify;"><em><strong>C&ugrave;ng l&agrave;m nh&eacute;:</strong></em></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 1:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-cjVhKQCSat8%2FUxmfFWTTtHI%2FAAAAAAAADk8%2FbdcNRys-YTI%2Fs1600%2F1.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-cjVhKQCSat8/UxmfFWTTtHI/AAAAAAAADk8/bdcNRys-YTI/s1600/1.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Trước ti&ecirc;n, c&aacute;c ấy cho xốp v&agrave;o phủ k&iacute;n gần miệng chậu.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 2:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-9ivIe5yn_2E%2FUxmfFzJtwuI%2FAAAAAAAADlI%2F6QVq64Z3U_I%2Fs1600%2F2.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9ivIe5yn_2E/UxmfFzJtwuI/AAAAAAAADlI/6QVq64Z3U_I/s1600/2.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Chọn mua những vi&ecirc;n chocolate nhỏ c&oacute; bọc giấy bạc v&agrave;o từng vi&ecirc;n n&egrave;.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 3:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-H1uxLddPCUU%2FUxmfF7Lzt5I%2FAAAAAAAADlA%2FqOlt7Ac4H24%2Fs1600%2F3.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-H1uxLddPCUU/UxmfF7Lzt5I/AAAAAAAADlA/qOlt7Ac4H24/s1600/3.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Lấy đầu nhọn xi&ecirc;n v&agrave;o giữa vi&ecirc;n chocolate như h&igrave;nh.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 4:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-OKIqTPlqG9Y%2FUxmfGrasg3I%2FAAAAAAAADlY%2FzJ7UlI7kbiQ%2Fs1600%2F4.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OKIqTPlqG9Y/UxmfGrasg3I/AAAAAAAADlY/zJ7UlI7kbiQ/s1600/4.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Cắt tờ giấy m&agrave;u theo k&iacute;ch thước 20 x 20 cm, d&ugrave;ng xi&ecirc;n tre chọc v&agrave;o giữa.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bước 5:</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-XJ9jXQlb0Jk%2FUxmfG6V3IfI%2FAAAAAAAADlU%2FkvKCoBN4PrI%2Fs1600%2F5.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-XJ9jXQlb0Jk/UxmfG6V3IfI/AAAAAAAADlU/kvKCoBN4PrI/s1600/5.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sau đ&oacute;, bạn t&uacute;m xung quanh gọn lại, d&ugrave;ng băng d&iacute;nh d&aacute;n cố định.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-8puM-Avy4VM%2FUxmfHaugU9I%2FAAAAAAAADlg%2FnMnaKHLycq0%2Fs1600%2F6.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-8puM-Avy4VM/UxmfHaugU9I/AAAAAAAADlg/nMnaKHLycq0/s1600/6.jpg" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Cắm từng b&ocirc;ng hoa chocolate v&agrave;o phủ k&iacute;n chậu l&agrave; xong.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="https://images-blogger-opensocial.googleusercontent.com/gadgets/proxy?url=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-jBqXeINqiy0%2FUxmflzThJ7I%2FAAAAAAAADls%2FbgRJ-t0bWhU%2Fs1600%2Fhoa-keo-chocolate.jpg&amp;container=blogger&amp;gadget=a&amp;rewriteMime=image%2F*" alt="" border="0" data-orig-src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-jBqXeINqiy0/UxmflzThJ7I/AAAAAAAADls/bgRJ-t0bWhU/s1600/hoa-keo-chocolate.jpg" /></p>
